<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> Except where this Regulation provides that decisions must be taken unanimously, the contract for the formation of a grouping may prescribe the conditions for a quorum and for a majority, in accordance with which the decisions, or some of them, shall be taken. </inglise>
