<inglise> Article 19 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 19 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> A grouping shall be managed by one or more natural persons appointed in the contract for the formation of the grouping or by decision of the members. </inglise>
