<inglise> If a Member State exercises this option, it must provide that the representative or representatives shall be liable as if they were themselves managers of the groupings concerned. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui liikmesriik seda v&otilde;imalust kasutab, peab ta s&auml;testama, et esindaja v&otilde;i esindajad kannavad sellist vastutust, nagu oleksid nad huvigrupi tegevjuhid. </eesti>
<inglise> The restrictions imposed in paragraph 1 shall also apply to those representatives. </inglise>
