<inglise> Article 21 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 21 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The profits resulting from a grouping's activities shall be deemed to be the profits of the members and shall be apportioned among them in the proportions laid down in the contract for the formation of the grouping or, in the absence of any such provision, in equal shares. </inglise>
