<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The members of a grouping shall contribute to the payment of the amount by which expenditure exceeds income in the proportions laid down in the contract for the formation of the grouping or, in the absence of any such provision, in equal shares. </inglise>
