<inglise> Article 24 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 24 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The members of a grouping shall have unlimited joint and several liability for its debts and other liabilities of whatever nature. </inglise>
