<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Creditors may not proceed against a member for payment in respect of debts and other liabilities, in accordance with the conditions laid down in paragraph 1, before the liquidation of a grouping is concluded, unless they have first requested the grouping to pay and payment has not been made within an appropriate period. </inglise>
