<inglise> Article 26 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 26 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> A decision to admit new members shall be taken unanimously by the members of the grouping. </inglise>
