<inglise> Article 27 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 27 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> A member of a grouping may withdraw in accordance with the conditions laid down in the contract for the formation of a grouping or, in the absence of such conditions, with the unanimous agreement of the other members. </inglise>
