<inglise> Any member of a grouping may, in addition, withdraw on just and proper grounds. </inglise>
<eesti> Lisaks v&otilde;ib iga liige v&auml;lja astuda, kui selleks on m&otilde;juv p&otilde;hjus. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Any member of a grouping may be expelled for the reasons listed in the contract for the formation of the grouping and, in any case, if he seriously fails in his obligations or if he causes or threatens to cause serious disruption in the operation of the grouping. </inglise>
